data.description: Need a charming Broadmoor home sweet home?  Here's one that's next to everything at a great price. Current owner has made it adorable and move-in ready just for you. It's clean, uncluttered and enchanting to allow you to easily envision your happy life here.  A block west of Youree Drive, you are walkable, bikeable in addition to an easy drive from shopping, restaurants, churches, and well, everything.  Beautiful original wood floors--NO CARPET throughout.  One of a few FOUR bedroom homes--fourth bedroom is perfect space for working from home.  VINYL SIDING EXTERIOR. NO FLOOD INSURANCE REQUIRED.  Neutral colors, updated and ready for new owners who value the 3 C's--character, charm and convenience--in this appealing and timeless core neighborhood.  Don't believe me--come see in person and feel delighted here.  It's one of the great ones you want to see now.
